## Design Token Usage

### Colors
All components now use semantic color tokens:
- `text-*`: `text-body`, `text-subtle`, `text-inverse`, `text-disabled`, `text-focus`
- `surface-*`: `surface-page`, `surface-card`, `surface-inverse`, `surface-disabled`, `surface-primary`, etc.
- `border-*`: `border-subtle`, `border-focus`, `border-disabled`
- `icon-*`: `icon-subtle`, `icon-display`, `icon-focus`

### Typography
All components use design token typography:
- Sizes: `text-xs` (12px), `text-sm` (14px), `text-base` (16px), `text-lg` (18px), `text-xl` (20px), `text-2xl` (24px)
- Weights: `font-medium` (500), `font-semibold` (600)
- Font family: `font-sans` (Plus Jakarta Sans)

### Spacing
- Uses design token spacing scale: `gap-1`, `gap-2`, `p-4`, `p-6`, `px-4`, `py-3`, etc.
- Button-specific: `button-gap`, `button-x-padding`, `button-y-padding` (via Tailwind spacing)

### Border Radius
- Uses `rounded` (4px) from design tokens
- Uses `rounded-lg` (8px) where appropriate
- Removed hardcoded `rounded-xl`, `rounded-2xl` in favor of design tokens

